<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />A fabulous fancy greeting between
close friends is the mark of a truly
special bond,<delay frames="13" /> don't you think?
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Well, that's why I think we should
have our own special greeting<tag a="110" b="0" />
just between the two of us.
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I've tried to come up with one that
suits us,<delay frames="13" /> but I'm drawing a blank<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Perhaps you have a clever idea? </message>
	<message label="001_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I think I've got it.</message>
	<message label="001_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">I'm drawing a blank.</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I just had the most wonderful idea!<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />You know how we sometimes say,<delay frames="13" />
"<tag a="110" b="14" />Don't YOU look fabulous today<endTag a="110" b="14" />"
as our special greeting?<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Well, I was thinking<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="13" /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />what if we put
our heads together and came up
with a brand-new greeting!
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />It's not that I don't like our current
greeting. It's lovely! <delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I just thought
it might be fun to shake things up.
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />But be honest, <tag a="110" b="3" />.<delay frames="13" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />What do YOU think?</message>
	<message label="002_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Let's try a new one.</message>
	<message label="002_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">I like it the way it is.</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Well, if it isn't <tag a="110" b="3" />.<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />You know, I was JUST thinking
about you.
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I was trying to decide what kind of
special greeting between friends is
the most fashionable this season<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="003_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ooh, I know!</message>
	<message label="003_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />Good luck with that.</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Why hello, <tag a="110" b="3" />!<delay frames="13" />
Perfect timing! <delay20 /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I was just thinking
about our special greeting.
You know how we love to say,
"<tag a="110" b="14" />Don't YOU look fabulous today<endTag a="110" b="14" />"?<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />It's beautiful, of course.<delay20 /> But I can't
help but think<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /> it might be nice to try
something a bit more<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="13" />sophisticated.
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Be honest, darling<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
What do you think?</message>
	<message label="004_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I've got an idea.</message>
	<message label="004_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">It's fine as it is.</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ah well,<delay frames="13" /> I suppose it happens to the
best of us, <tag a="110" b="6" />.<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I've been wracking my brain all day,<delay frames="13" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />but I simply canNOT come up with
the perfect greeting for us.</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Oh, do you?<delay frames="13" /> Well, yes. I understand.<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I, too, have grown fond of our
current greeting.<delay frames="13" /> It's so US!
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />That settles it, then.<delay frames="13" /> <anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />We'll go on
saying our wonderful saying in
our wonderful way, <tag a="110" b="6" />.
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Thank you for reminding me that
there's no need to tamper with
perfection, <tag a="110" b="3" />.</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Oh<tag a="110" b="0" />um, thank you?<delay20 /> <anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I suppose
I do need all the luck I can get.<pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I've been trying to think of a unique
and stylish greeting for just you and
me<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />and had NO luck, <tag a="110" b="6" />.</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />You really think so?<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Well,<delay frames="13" /> I certainly haven't been able
to dream up anything better than
"<tag a="110" b="14" />Don't YOU look fabulous today<endTag a="110" b="14" />."
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Forget it, <tag a="110" b="6" />! <delay frames="13" />Who needs
a sophisticated greeting <delay20 /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />when we
have the PERFECT greeting already!</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Well let's hear it, then!</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Alrighty! Let's try it out<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="14" />Don't YOU look fabulous today<endTag a="110" b="14" />!<delay40 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Well<tag a="110" b="0" />what do you think?</message>
	<message label="101_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">I like it!</message>
	<message label="101_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">It's a little off...</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />"<tag a="110" b="14" />Don't YOU look fabulous today<endTag a="110" b="14" />"?<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Hmm<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="13" /> <anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />So, you want to keep our
greeting the way it is, then?</message>
	<message label="102_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">Yes. Let's keep it!</message>
	<message label="102_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">No. Let's change it.</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Oh!<delay frames="13" /> I see.<delay20 /> Well then,<delay frames="13" /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /> tell me again.
We'll get it this time!</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Oh dear,<delay20 /> fretting over what to pick?<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Take your time,<delay8 /> there's no rush.<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Shall we give it another try?</message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="14" />Don't YOU look fabulous today<endTag a="110" b="14" />!<10_4 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Yes! That sounds wonderful!</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="14" />Don't YOU look fabulous today<endTag a="110" b="14" />!<10_4 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Yes!<delay frames="13" /> Well done!<delay frames="13" /> It's absolutely
perfect!</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Well, <tag a="110" b="3" />, <delay frames="13" />our new
greeting is decided. I hope you're
as pleased as I am, <tag a="110" b="6" />.</message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />It's the very best greeting for the
very best of friends.<delay20 /> <anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I feel closer
to you than ever, <tag a="110" b="6" />.</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />A tailor-made greeting! Just for us!<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I'm so VERY excited to try it out,
<tag a="110" b="6" />!</message>
	<message label="300" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Wonderful! <delay frames="13" />We shall continue to say,<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />"<tag a="110" b="14" />Don't YOU look fabulous today<endTag a="110" b="14" />."<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
It's settled, <tag a="110" b="6" />.</message>
	<message label="301" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Hahaha! <delay20 />Oh <tag a="110" b="3" />,<delay frames="13" /> <anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />you
really do like our special greeting,
don't you?
I mean, <anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />why mess with the
best, <tag a="110" b="6" />?</message>
	<message label="302" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Oh, I understand completely.<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />"<tag a="110" b="14" />Don't YOU look fabulous today<endTag a="110" b="14" />"
evokes so many fond memories!
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I'm sorry I ever doubted our special
greeting.<delay20 /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /> Let's just pretend this
never happened, <tag a="110" b="6" />.</message>
</msbt>